  if (data.nationality === defaultCountry && !data.geo_organization) {
    ctx.addIssue({ path: ["geo_organization"], message: t("geo_organization_required"), code: z.ZodIssueCode.custom });
  }
  // ...other custom checks...
});
```

This way, all your custom logic runs regardless of base validation status, and you can aggregate all errors for the user in one go. For more, see the [Zod v4 API docs on `.check()`](https://zod.dev/api#check) and [error formatting utilities](https://zod.dev/error-formatting).

