//   type: 'object',
//   properties: { name: { type: 'string' }, friend: { '$ref': '#' } },
//   required: [ 'name', 'friend' ],
//   additionalProperties: false,
// }
```

If instead you want to throw an error, set the `cycles` option to `"throw"` .

```
z.toJSONSchema(User, { cycles: "throw" });
// => throws Error
```
